title: Ethan Deiss
description:
Quick edit of Trollhaugen local Ethan Deiss. As a snowboarder, Ethan is known for throwing it down in the streets, but that doesn't mean he can't send it during a contest. When the snow starts falling, Ethan backs the new Arnette Skylight.

Stay in touch with Arnette for giveaways, as well as new team and product updates at www.facebook.com/arnette and www.arnette.com.
